headline: Citi raises Super Micro target, but warns on margin pressures
summary: Investing.com -- Citi raised its price target on Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ:SMCI) to $52 from $37 a share in a note Friday, citing improving demand for AI servers and the ramp of Nvidia’s GB200/300 platforms.
